### 3.2 Метрики — Prometheus / VictoriaMetrics

#### Вариант A: ServiceMonitor (Kubernetes + Prometheus Operator)

```yaml
# Service
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: order-service
  labels:
    app: order-service
spec:
  selector:
    app: order-service
  ports:
    - name: http-metrics
      port: 8080
      targetPort: 8080

---
# ServiceMonitor
apiVersion: monitoring.coreos.com/v1
kind: ServiceMonitor
metadata:
  name: order-service
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    release: prometheus
spec:
  namespaceSelector:
    matchNames:
      - production
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: order-service
  endpoints:
    - port: http-metrics
      path: /actuator/prometheus
      interval: 15s
      scrapeTimeout: 10s
```

#### Вариант B: prometheus.yml (Docker Compose / VM)

```yaml
scrape_configs:
  - job_name: order-service
    metrics_path: /actuator/prometheus
    scrape_interval: 15s
    static_configs:
      - targets: ['order-service:8080']
        labels:
          service: order-service
          environment: prod
```

#### Проверка

```bash
# Метрики
curl -s http://order-service:8080/actuator/prometheus | head -20

# Liveness
curl -s http://order-service:8080/actuator/health/liveness

# Readiness
curl -s http://order-service:8080/actuator/health/readiness
```

